    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="1-使用Pacman主题">1.使用Pacman主题</h4>
<h4 id="2-添加多说评论">2.添加多说评论</h4>
<h4 id="3-文章重复现象解决办法：">3.文章重复现象解决办法：</h4>
<p>删除博客根目录下的db.jason</p>
<h4 id="4-在variable-styl文件中修改主题配色">4.在variable.styl文件中修改主题配色</h4>
<figure class="highlight {bash}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">color</span>-blue = <span class="preprocessor">#20b2aa ##修改标题颜色为浅海洋绿</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">color</span>-theme = <span class="preprocessor">#20b2aa ##修改主题基础颜色为浅海洋绿</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="5-将博客URL提交到搜索引擎:">5.将博客URL提交到搜索引擎:</h4>
<p>将搜索引擎的meta验证标签复制到 hexo\themes\pacman\layout_partial\head.ejs的head中</p>
<h4 id="6-使用百度统计:">6.使用百度统计:</h4>
<ul>
<li><p>参考文章：<a href="http://www.tuicool.com/articles/AfQnQjy" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo你的博客</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>编辑文件 hexo\themes\pacman_config.yml, 增加配置项：</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight {bash}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">baidu_tongji</span>: <span class="string">true</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>新建文件 hexo\themes\pacman\layout_partial\baidu_tongji.ejs, 内容如下：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight {bash}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="vbscript">&lt;% <span class="keyword">if</span> (theme.baidu_tongji){ %&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="title">script</span> <span class="attribute">type</span>=<span class="value">"text/javascript"</span>&gt;</span><span class="javascript"></span></div><div class="line">#我的百度统计代码</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="title">script</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="vbscript">&lt;% } %&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>编辑文件 hexo\themes\modernist\layout_partial\head.ejs, 在<head>之前增加：</head></li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight {bash}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;<span class="variable">%-</span> partial(<span class="string">'baidu_tongji'</span>) <span class="variable">%&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
